PHP
===

Tag names following PHP version.

Branches
--------
- 7.0-apache
- 7.0-cli
- 7.0-fpm
- 5.6-apache
- 5.6-cli
- 5.6-fpm

To use the latest php version available for a branch, use:
```
docker pull leandrosilva/php:7.0-apache
```

or a specific php version (check the tags):
```
docker pull leandrosilva/php:7.0.7-apache
```

PHP extensions included
-----------------------

In all versions:
- apcu
- ctype
- dom
- fileinfo
- gd
- intl
- json
- mbstring
- mcrypt
- mysqli
- oci8
- opcache
- pcntl
- pdo
- pdo_mysql
- pdo_pgsql
- phar
- simplexml
- xdebug
- zip

Only in 7.0 branch:
- bcmath
 
Only in 5.6 branch:
- mssql

Extras installed
----------------

- Composer
- vim

